---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
  <article class="policy">
    <h2>Privacy &amp; Cookies Policy</h2>

    <p>
      This website uses Google Analytics 4 (GA4) to better understand how visitors use the site.
      Analytics tracking is optional and controlled by the cookie banner.
    </p>

    <h3>What We Collect</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Pages viewed and navigation path</li>
      <li>Basic engagement events (for example: clicks, downloads, and scroll depth)</li>
      <li>General technical details (browser/device information provided by GA4)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How We Use It</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Understand which content is most useful</li>
      <li>Improve site structure and usability</li>
      <li>Measure interest in projects, blog posts, and contact links</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Cookie Consent Choices</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Accept</strong>: enables GA4 analytics cookies</li>
      <li><strong>Decline</strong>: keeps analytics disabled</li>
      <li>Your choice is saved in your browser and reused on future visits</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Manage or Change Consent</h3>
    <p>
      If you want to change your choice later, clear site data for this domain in your browser settings,
      then reload the page to see the consent banner again.
    </p>

    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:me@wyliefisher.com">me@wyliefisher.com</a>
    </p>

    <p class="updated">Last updated: February 23, 2026</p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .policy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .policy ul {
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .updated {
    font-size: var(--fontSize-secondary);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
